        "AI and Technical Limitations": "AI \u0914\u0930 technical limitations",
        "MIT PRO may use AI, automation, image analysis, timing interpretation, market-state logic, and protection rules. AI outputs, market-state readings, confidence scores, timing indicators, trap warnings, and protection alerts may be delayed, incomplete, inaccurate, or unavailable. Users must independently verify all information.": "MIT PRO AI, automation, image analysis, timing interpretation, market-state logic \u0914\u0930 protection rules \u0915\u093e \u0909\u092a\u092f\u094b\u0917 \u0915\u0930 \u0938\u0915\u0924\u093e \u0939\u0948\u0964 AI outputs, market-state readings, confidence scores, timing indicators, trap warnings \u0914\u0930 protection alerts delayed, incomplete, inaccurate \u092f\u093e unavailable \u0939\u094b \u0938\u0915\u0924\u0947 \u0939\u0948\u0902\u0964 \u0909\u092a\u092f\u094b\u0917\u0915\u0930\u094d\u0924\u093e\u0913\u0902 \u0915\u094b \u0938\u092d\u0940 \u091c\u093e\u0928\u0915\u093e\u0930\u0940 independently verify \u0915\u0930\u0928\u0940 \u091a\u093e\u0939\u093f\u090f\u0964",
