        "License Activation": "Lisans Aktivasyonu",
        "Users move from the command center into a focused license request flow with manual USDT verification, admin review, and support visibility.": "Kullan\u0131c\u0131lar komuta merkezinden manuel USDT do\u011frulamas\u0131, y\u00f6netici incelemesi ve destek g\u00f6r\u00fcn\u00fcrl\u00fc\u011f\u00fc ile odaklanm\u0131\u015f bir lisans iste\u011fi ak\u0131\u015f\u0131na ge\u00e7er.",
        "Open License Activation": "Lisans Aktivasyonunu A\u00e7",
        "Contact MIT PRO Team": "MIT PRO Ekibiyle \u0130leti\u015fime Ge\u00e7in",
        "MIT PRO was created to become a layer of protection, education, and awareness in a world where many people are influenced by noise, misinformation, emotional reactions, unrealistic promises, and manipulation.": "MIT PRO, bir\u00e7ok insan\u0131n g\u00fcr\u00fclt\u00fcden, yanl\u0131\u015f bilgilerden, duygusal tepkilerden, ger\u00e7ek\u00e7i olmayan vaatlerden ve manip\u00fclasyondan etkilendi\u011fi bir d\u00fcnyada bir koruma, e\u011fitim ve fark\u0131ndal\u0131k katman\u0131 olmak i\u00e7in yarat\u0131ld\u0131.",
        "We believe that knowledge should come before action, discipline should come before emotion, and understanding should come before decision-making.": "Bilginin eylemden, disiplinin duygudan, anlay\u0131\u015f\u0131n karar vermeden \u00f6nce gelmesi gerekti\u011fine inan\u0131yoruz.",
        "MIT PRO is not built to encourage impulsive behavior. It is built to help users understand what is happening, why it is happening, and when caution may be more important than action.": "MIT PRO d\u00fcrt\u00fcsel davran\u0131\u015flar\u0131 te\u015fvik etmek i\u00e7in tasarlanmam\u0131\u015ft\u0131r. Kullan\u0131c\u0131lar\u0131n neler oldu\u011funu, neden oldu\u011funu ve tedbirin ne zaman eyleme ge\u00e7mekten daha \u00f6nemli olabilece\u011fini anlamalar\u0131na yard\u0131mc\u0131 olmak i\u00e7in olu\u015fturulmu\u015ftur.",
        "We promise to continuously build technology that helps users learn more, understand more, protect more, think better, and decide smarter.": "Kullan\u0131c\u0131lar\u0131n daha fazla \u00f6\u011frenmesine, daha fazla anlamas\u0131na, daha fazla korunmas\u0131na, daha iyi d\u00fc\u015f\u00fcnmesine ve daha ak\u0131ll\u0131ca karar vermesine yard\u0131mc\u0131 olacak teknolojiyi s\u00fcrekli olarak geli\u015ftirece\u011fimize s\u00f6z veriyoruz.",
        "Every day, individuals navigate uncertainty, information overload, and rapidly changing conditions. MIT Pro exists to promote awareness, discipline, and informed decision-making through intelligence and protection.": "Her gün bireyler belirsizlik, bilgi yoğunluğu ve hızla değişen koşullar içinde yol alır. MIT Pro, zeka ve koruma yoluyla farkındalığı, disiplini ve bilinçli karar vermeyi desteklemek için vardır.",
        "The first responsibility of intelligence is protection. Before looking for opportunities, users should understand risk, instability, uncertainty, and changing conditions.": "\u0130stihbarat\u0131n ilk sorumlulu\u011fu korumad\u0131r. F\u0131rsatlar\u0131 aramadan \u00f6nce kullan\u0131c\u0131lar\u0131n riski, istikrars\u0131zl\u0131\u011f\u0131, belirsizli\u011fi ve de\u011fi\u015fen ko\u015fullar\u0131 anlamalar\u0131 gerekir.",
        "Long-term improvement comes from learning and understanding, not emotional reaction or short-term excitement. Every interaction should increase awareness.": "Uzun vadeli geli\u015fme, duygusal tepki veya k\u0131sa vadeli heyecandan de\u011fil, \u00f6\u011frenme ve anlamadan gelir. Her etkile\u015fim fark\u0131ndal\u0131\u011f\u0131 artt\u0131rmal\u0131d\u0131r.",
        "Technology should support human judgment, not replace it. MIT PRO combines adaptive intelligence systems with human validation so users remain in control.": "Teknoloji insan muhakemesini desteklemeli, onun yerini almamal\u0131. MIT PRO, uyarlanabilir zeka sistemlerini insan do\u011frulamas\u0131yla birle\u015ftirerek kontrol\u00fcn kullan\u0131c\u0131lar\u0131n elinde kalmas\u0131n\u0131 sa\u011flar.",
        "Users deserve clarity. MIT PRO explains conditions, confidence levels, risks, and reasoning in a way that promotes understanding rather than blind reliance.": "Kullan\u0131c\u0131lar netli\u011fi hak ediyor. MIT PRO ko\u015fullar\u0131, g\u00fcven d\u00fczeylerini, riskleri ve ak\u0131l y\u00fcr\u00fctmeyi k\u00f6r\u00fc k\u00f6r\u00fcne g\u00fcven yerine anlay\u0131\u015f\u0131 te\u015fvik edecek \u015fekilde a\u00e7\u0131klar.",
        "Markets, technology, and user behavior evolve. MIT PRO is committed to improving intelligence, protection mechanisms, education, and user experience.": "Pazarlar, teknoloji ve kullan\u0131c\u0131 davran\u0131\u015flar\u0131 geli\u015fiyor. MIT PRO, istihbarat\u0131, koruma mekanizmalar\u0131n\u0131, e\u011fitimi ve kullan\u0131c\u0131 deneyimini iyile\u015ftirmeye kendini adam\u0131\u015ft\u0131r.",
        "To become the world's most trusted Market Intelligence Terminal, empowering individuals through education, awareness, adaptive intelligence, and human-centered protection.": "Bireyleri e\u011fitim, fark\u0131ndal\u0131k, uyarlanabilir zeka ve insan merkezli koruma yoluyla g\u00fc\u00e7lendiren, d\u00fcnyan\u0131n en g\u00fcvenilir Piyasa \u0130stihbarat Terminali olmak.",
        "\"Knowledge Before Action. Protection Before Emotion. Understanding Before Every Decision.\"": "\"Eylemden \u00d6nce Bilgi. Duygudan \u00d6nce Koruma. Her Karardan \u00d6nce Anlay\u0131\u015f.\"",
