        "Continuously interprets market structure, liquidity behavior, timing context, and evolving market conditions to assist user awareness.": "Kullan\u0131c\u0131 fark\u0131ndal\u0131\u011f\u0131na yard\u0131mc\u0131 olmak i\u00e7in piyasa yap\u0131s\u0131n\u0131, likidite davran\u0131\u015f\u0131n\u0131, zamanlama ba\u011flam\u0131n\u0131 ve geli\u015fen piyasa ko\u015fullar\u0131n\u0131 s\u00fcrekli olarak yorumlar.",
        "Arjun Defense System": "Arjun Savunma Sistemi",
        "Designed to promote discipline through session controls, cooldown protection, behavioral safeguards, and capital preservation tools.": "Oturum kontrolleri, bekleme s\u00fcresi korumas\u0131, davran\u0131\u015fsal \u00f6nlemler ve sermaye koruma ara\u00e7lar\u0131 arac\u0131l\u0131\u011f\u0131yla disiplini te\u015fvik etmek i\u00e7in tasarlanm\u0131\u015ft\u0131r.",
