        "Attach USDT payment proof only if payment is already completed. PNG, JPG, WEBP, or PDF up to 5 MB.": "Yaln\u0131zca \u00f6deme zaten tamamlanm\u0131\u015fsa USDT \u00f6deme kan\u0131t\u0131n\u0131 ekleyin. 5 MB'a kadar PNG, JPG, WEBP veya PDF.",
