        "Payment details are verified before any license code is issued.": "\u00d6deme ayr\u0131nt\u0131lar\u0131 herhangi bir lisans kodu verilmeden \u00f6nce do\u011frulan\u0131r.",
        "Stripe will be added later. Current public purchase flow is USDT manual confirmation only.": "\u015eerit daha sonra eklenecektir. Mevcut halka a\u00e7\u0131k sat\u0131n alma ak\u0131\u015f\u0131 yaln\u0131zca USDT'nin manuel onay\u0131d\u0131r.",
        "Phone / WhatsApp": "Telefon / WhatsApp",
        "Payment reference optional": "\u00d6deme referans\u0131 iste\u011fe ba\u011fl\u0131",
        "Optional message. Example: I want Commander Access and will pay through USDT TRC20.": "\u0130ste\u011fe ba\u011fl\u0131 mesaj. \u00d6rnek: Komutan Eri\u015fimi istiyorum ve USDT TRC20 arac\u0131l\u0131\u011f\u0131yla \u00f6deme yapaca\u011f\u0131m.",
        "MIT PRO is an educational, informational, observation, market-intelligence, trader-protection, and decision-support platform. It is not financial advice, not a broker, not an investment adviser, and not an outcome-assurance service.": "MIT PRO bir e\u011fitim, bilgilendirme, g\u00f6zlem, piyasa istihbarat\u0131, yat\u0131r\u0131mc\u0131 koruma ve karar destek platformudur. Finansal tavsiye de\u011fildir, komisyoncu de\u011fildir, yat\u0131r\u0131m dan\u0131\u015fman\u0131 de\u011fildir ve sonu\u00e7 g\u00fcvence hizmeti de\u011fildir.",
        "Trading and market participation involve risk. Users may lose some or all of their funds. Users should not trade money they cannot afford to lose.": "Ticaret ve piyasaya kat\u0131l\u0131m risk i\u00e7erir. Kullan\u0131c\u0131lar fonlar\u0131n\u0131n bir k\u0131sm\u0131n\u0131 veya tamam\u0131n\u0131 kaybedebilir. Kullan\u0131c\u0131lar kaybetmeyi g\u00f6ze alamayacaklar\u0131 parayla ticaret yapmamal\u0131d\u0131r.",
        "MIT PRO does not provide financial, investment, legal, tax, brokerage, or professional trading advice. Information shown by MIT PRO is for educational, informational, observation, and decision-support purposes only.": "MIT PRO finansal, yat\u0131r\u0131m, hukuk, vergi, komisyonculuk veya profesyonel ticaret tavsiyeleri sa\u011flamaz. MIT PRO taraf\u0131ndan g\u00f6sterilen bilgiler yaln\u0131zca e\u011fitim, bilgilendirme, g\u00f6zlem ve karar destek ama\u00e7l\u0131d\u0131r.",
        "MIT PRO does not guarantee profits, income, trading accuracy, successful outcomes, or loss prevention. Any market analysis, alerts, confidence levels, examples, screenshots, demos, or historical references do not guarantee future results.": "MIT PRO k\u00e2r\u0131, geliri, ticaretin do\u011frulu\u011funu, ba\u015far\u0131l\u0131 sonu\u00e7lar\u0131 veya zarar \u00f6nlemeyi garanti etmez. Herhangi bir piyasa analizi, uyar\u0131lar, g\u00fcven d\u00fczeyleri, \u00f6rnekler, ekran g\u00f6r\u00fcnt\u00fcleri, demolar veya ge\u00e7mi\u015f referanslar gelecekteki sonu\u00e7lar\u0131 garanti etmez.",
        "MIT PRO does not place trades, execute orders, manage funds, control brokerage accounts, or make final trading decisions for users. Every decision remains the sole responsibility of the user.": "MIT PRO, kullan\u0131c\u0131lar i\u00e7in i\u015flem yapmaz, emir yerine getirmez, fonlar\u0131 y\u00f6netmez, arac\u0131l\u0131k hesaplar\u0131n\u0131 kontrol etmez veya nihai i\u015flem kararlar\u0131 vermez. Her karar tamamen kullan\u0131c\u0131n\u0131n sorumlulu\u011fundad\u0131r.",
        "MIT PRO is not a broker, exchange, financial institution, investment adviser, fund manager, portfolio manager, managed trading service, or copy-trading service.": "MIT PRO bir komisyoncu, borsa, finans kurumu, yat\u0131r\u0131m dan\u0131\u015fman\u0131, fon y\u00f6neticisi, portf\u00f6y y\u00f6neticisi, y\u00f6netilen ticaret hizmeti veya kopya ticaret hizmeti de\u011fildir.",
        "Market conditions can change quickly. Any analysis, AI output, intelligence health indicator, confidence score, market state reading, timing indicator, risk warning, or protection alert may be delayed, incomplete, inaccurate, or affected by data, timing, platform, technical, or market limitations.": "Piyasa ko\u015fullar\u0131 h\u0131zla de\u011fi\u015febilir. Herhangi bir analiz, yapay zeka \u00e7\u0131kt\u0131s\u0131, istihbarat sa\u011fl\u0131k g\u00f6stergesi, g\u00fcven puan\u0131, piyasa durumu okumas\u0131, zamanlama g\u00f6stergesi, risk uyar\u0131s\u0131 veya koruma uyar\u0131s\u0131 gecikebilir, eksik, hatal\u0131 olabilir veya verilerden, zamanlamadan, platformdan, teknik veya pazar s\u0131n\u0131rlamalar\u0131ndan etkilenebilir.",
        "Forex, OTC markets, crypto, derivatives, binary-style products, leveraged instruments, and other speculative markets may carry high risk and may not be suitable for all users.": "Forex, OTC piyasalar\u0131, kripto, t\u00fcrevler, ikili stil \u00fcr\u00fcnler, kald\u0131ra\u00e7l\u0131 ara\u00e7lar ve di\u011fer spek\u00fclatif piyasalar y\u00fcksek risk ta\u015f\u0131yabilir ve t\u00fcm kullan\u0131c\u0131lar i\u00e7in uygun olmayabilir.",
        "Users are responsible for understanding the risks, complying with local laws, following broker/platform rules, and making their own independent decisions. Users must independently verify all information before acting.": "Kullan\u0131c\u0131lar riskleri anlamaktan, yerel yasalara uymaktan, komisyoncu/platform kurallar\u0131na uymaktan ve kendi ba\u011f\u0131ms\u0131z kararlar\u0131n\u0131 vermekten sorumludur. Kullan\u0131c\u0131lar harekete ge\u00e7meden \u00f6nce t\u00fcm bilgileri ba\u011f\u0131ms\u0131z olarak do\u011frulamal\u0131d\u0131r.",
        "Past performance, demo results, backtests, examples, user feedback, screenshots, or testimonials do not guarantee future results.": "Ge\u00e7mi\u015f performans, demo sonu\u00e7lar\u0131, geriye d\u00f6n\u00fck testler, \u00f6rnekler, kullan\u0131c\u0131 geri bildirimleri, ekran g\u00f6r\u00fcnt\u00fcleri veya referanslar gelecekteki sonu\u00e7lar\u0131 garanti etmez.",
        "To the maximum extent permitted by applicable law, MIT PRO and its team are not liable for trading losses, missed opportunities, platform issues, user decisions, broker issues, market volatility, technical delays, data errors, or misuse of the platform.": "Ge\u00e7erli yasalar\u0131n izin verdi\u011fi azami \u00f6l\u00e7\u00fcde, MIT PRO ve ekibi ticari kay\u0131plardan, ka\u00e7\u0131r\u0131lan f\u0131rsatlardan, platform sorunlar\u0131ndan, kullan\u0131c\u0131 kararlar\u0131ndan, komisyoncu sorunlar\u0131ndan, piyasa oynakl\u0131\u011f\u0131ndan, teknik gecikmelerden, veri hatalar\u0131ndan veya platformun k\u00f6t\u00fcye kullan\u0131lmas\u0131ndan sorumlu de\u011fildir.",
        "For questions, contact": "Sorular\u0131n\u0131z i\u00e7in ileti\u015fime ge\u00e7in",
        "MIT PRO Data Protection": "MIT PRO Veri Koruma",
        "This Privacy Policy explains how MIT PRO may collect, use, store, protect, and process user information.": "Bu Gizlilik Politikas\u0131, MIT PRO'nun kullan\u0131c\u0131 bilgilerini nas\u0131l toplayabilece\u011fini, kullanabilece\u011fini, saklayabilece\u011fini, koruyabilece\u011fini ve i\u015fleyebilece\u011fini a\u00e7\u0131klamaktad\u0131r.",
        "License Security": "Lisans G\u00fcvenli\u011fi",
